{"tid":2394765,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"禁止中共大外宣！　英通訊局撤銷央視「中國環球電視網」播放牌照","createTime":"2021-02-04T11:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T13:27:10.000Z","uid":204533,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e1159f66387ff5a0e8efbdb3a56f548fc7f84b7f","tid":2394765,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:49:20.000Z","msg":"英國通訊管理局（Ofcom）今天（4日）宣佈撤銷中國官媒、央視旗下中國環球電視網（CGTN）在英國的播放牌照，因為經調查後證實CGTN的持照者並沒有編輯監督權，裁定CGTN與中國共產黨有關聯，違反了英國法律。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">英國通訊管理局在聲明中表示，根據英國廣播法例，持照人必須能夠控制牌照列明的服務，包括擁有播放節目的編輯監督權，而且牌照持有人不能由政治機構控制。但當局調查後證實，CGTN目前牌照持有人星空華文傳媒電影有限公司（Star China Media Limited ，SCML），無權選擇或編訂CGTN的節目編排，只是CGTN英國服務的經銷商，而非服務「供應者」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">聲明並指，「我們無法批准發放牌照給CGTN，因為該台最終仍是被中國共產黨所掌控，而這違反了英國廣播法」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n星空華文傳媒電影有限公司任何一位員工似乎都沒有參與CGTN的任何決策或日常營運，CGTN也確定其全球編輯委員會是節目選擇及組織的最終決策者。因此星空華文傳媒電影有限公司並不符合發牌法律要求，也就不是合法的廣播持照人。<br />\n<br />\n英國通訊管理局去年指CGTN違反了《 Ofcom廣播守則》，沒有在報導香港示威運動時保持應有公正性，並且還嚴重違反公平和隱私規則，並表示會考慮向CGTN實施制裁，當局在聲明中強調，今天的決定不會影響對CGTN的制裁程序，「我們預計很快會做出決定」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">英國通訊管理局仍對CGTN三起報導展開調查，包括播出駐港總領事館前職員鄭文傑的認罪片段。</span></strong>（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"bb813fba6af6d603104fe10c3f2c5ad219482239","tid":2394765,"uid":52358,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:51:20.000Z","msg":"等睇CCTVB聽日吠足成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f9e0845645cda8813c4ed4adf916ea0e0df3f2","tid":2394765,"uid":204533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:51:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210204/X6N7XBVYGJFHHHW4RYJTP5226I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210204%2FX6N7XBVYGJFHHHW4RYJTP5226I%2F&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRCNNnhsiPIcvur842Fp1uB0%3D&h=5fe3eaa6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210204%2FX6N7XBVYGJFHHHW4RYJTP5226I%2F&h=87dc0acc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210204/X6N7XBVYGJFHHHW4RYJTP5226I/</a>"},{"pid":"8bb553e2e5a39f5d8399848cd9bfadad4757b410","tid":2394765,"uid":254594,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:58:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LNLODOTQTTTRMQGCOFOGJFBQOI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLNLODOTQTTTRMQGCOFOGJFBQOI.jpg&h=ba178a5c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adfd41dd15d4cfae312df35d0965e75a650f0de6","tid":2394765,"uid":186079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:59:06.000Z","msg":"日出國"},{"pid":"f928219dd1085b6b5848bd0c6b4590c8a1d513ad","tid":2394765,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T12:00:43.000Z","msg":"日出得好快"},{"pid":"409baff6fd8579b91d53aa39f5549d83225cbac9","tid":2394765,"uid":272952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T12:01:04.000Z","msg":"石頭&hellip;&hellip;腳"},{"pid":"4676a3fa3e38029d383a483f6728fec2e27828bc","tid":2394765,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T12:07:15.000Z","msg":"自己攞嚟衰"},{"pid":"039830a691f95cab7cec9909c33806fe1131011c","tid":2394765,"uid":52215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T12:36:15.000Z","msg":"禁返BBC係中國香港轉播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707a2589fb55228cb64e0cecabb926c0f7c3acf9","tid":2394765,"uid":78295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T12:38:48.000Z","msg":"祖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff4ae5783021af676ddfc04138fcfc